title: Bassel al-Assad Stadium (Al-Hasakah)
text: Bassel al-Assad Stadium () is a <a href="multi-purpose%20stadium">multi-purpose stadium</a> in <a href="Al-Hasakah">Al-Hasakah</a>. It is currently used mostly for <a href="association%20football">football</a> matches. The stadium has a capacity of 25,000 spectators.
